; OpenADS ACE-compatible DLL exports.
; Reported by JONSSON RUSSI (RusSoft Ltda).
;
; All entry points use the Microsoft __cdecl convention (the SAP ACE
; default on Windows). Names are exported undecorated on x64 and x86;
; __cdecl on x86 prepends a leading underscore at link time, but the
; .def NAME form forces the public export to match the source name.
;
; NOTE: For x86 Harbour (rddads) compatibility, use openads_ace_x86.def
; which exports __stdcall-decorated (@N) names instead.
